&lt;p&gt;Northern Lincolnshire and Goole NHS Foundation Trust are looking to recruit a Principal Information Analyst to be a lead analyst within the Information Services team. Working with the Senior Information Manager along with other Analysts within the team, the role will key key to shaping information provision, supporting decision making, and understanding the Trust&#39;s data flows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Information Service’s Department is responsible for the provision of strategic, tactical and operational information management across the Trust. The successful candidate will be responsible for the Trust’s performance returns, along with data flows in and out of the team, both external to the Trust and internal.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alex Bell, Head of Information Services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address alex.bell1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please email Alex Bell or Phil Croft on alex.bell1@nhs.net or philip.croft@nhs.net to ask questions, or arrange a call.&lt;/p&gt;
